<br />\n嗰一年又見過係醫院識嘅院友仙遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係鬼門關走出黎之後更加享受人生，有咩想做就去做。<br />\n因為覺得人唔一定活到8,90先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8303f88df7787fd9e380141e70d62197bf7ea1d","tid":1913112,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"Take care sis"},{"pid":"aa6080b34a4334ce30d427c7688739f1615afd8b","tid":1913112,"uid":120123,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"加油....<br />\n我日日見到d cancer patients......<br />\n後生又有，老又有，咁當然老的多。但見到佢地，我有時又會覺得冇病冇痛其實已經好幸運。健康唔係必然的事。<br />\n搵幾多，生活點都好，最重要真係健康。<br />\n<br />\n希望樓主早日康復"},{"pid":"419d27832587576b980ad478f67685f4692d9e3a","tid":1913112,"uid":118692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"take care and add oil <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f217ca38003f72b40f3de8ecadb1534a41179f","tid":1913112,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"好多人有錢 但無健康 好多人好窮 都身體好好 不停做"},{"pid":"57fa10cfcbfbfb779edbd4f488fe52ec1d2eeff0","tid":1913112,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"世界要你努力去考取功名 但是真誠才是最大本領～～<br />\n<br />\n路過，祝樓主以後會順利平安"},{"pid":"9546ea4c5d26a2f16411b399cc5cb328d7aa24c8","tid":1913112,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd68b1ce08613594433acd5ed6807d2882e0e4c","tid":1913112,"uid":65754,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:47:09.000Z","msg":"29歲確診鼻咽癌2B期<br />\n捱過3次化療加33次電療<br />\n依家完成療程已經過咗8年，仲有2年觀察期就正式康復<br />\n<br />\n加油💪🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cf